==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhallowed
<hw>Un*hal"lowed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>hallowed</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not consecrated;
hence, profane; unholy; impious; wicked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the cause of truth, no <qex>unhallowed</qex> violence . . . is
either necessary or admissible.</q> <rj><qau>E. D.
Griffin.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhand</ent>⟦br⟧
